Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Average delay in starting 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed' without 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases with more than one occurrence of this activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases that follow the variant ending in 'Completed + Resolved -> Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the fastest case to resolution
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the slowest case to resolution
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases that also involve 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation occurs

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' against 'Accepted + Assigned' for cases leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total elapsed time involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all variants where it appears
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Average time from the start of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to the end of the process for cases including 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
